            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_47wh' title='Col. 47WH &mdash; HC Deb 24 February 2004 vol 418 c47WH' name='column_47wh' href='#column_47wh' rel='bookmark'>47WH</a>
            This has been an important debate and there are many questions to be answered. I hope that the Minister will continually review the whole process, as there will be changing aspects and further questions as we go along. Most of all, we must respect the fact that many people are troubled and damaged as a consequence of a miscarriage of justice.
